-- Merkel Thanks Sarkozy for Close Collaboration During Debt Crisis
-- B y   A l e x   W e b b
-- 2012-05-07T20:25:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-07/merkel-thanks-sarkozy-for-close-collaboration-during-debt-crisis.html
Angela Merkel  telephoned outgoing
French President Nicolas Sarkozy this evening to thank him for
his “close and trustworthy” collaboration in combating the
European debt crisis, according to a German government
statement.  The German chancellor and Sarkozy are both convinced that
“Germany and France will continue to bear the responsibility to
promote a united Europe through working together,”  the
government added in the e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alex Webb in Frankfurt at 
 awebb25@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chad Thomas at   cthomas16@bloomberg.net . 